aySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"真的呢……只是越過了一扇門\n感覺就好像到了不同的世界一樣……\n而且身體會一直暖暖的呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"這就是三溫暖的魅力喔……\n從身體裡都開始熱起來，\n流了很多汗之後就會覺得非常清爽喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"清爽啊……這麼一說，\n好像還是第一次流了這麼多汗呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"雖然演奏中也會流一些汗，\n但跟三溫暖好像又不太一樣耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"我懂，會嚇到說\n原來是可以流出這麼多汗的啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"多虧這樣，該說是放心了下來嗎……\n總覺得有種輕飄飄又很舒服的感覺……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"可以讓你們兩位也知道三溫暖的魅力\n真是太令人高興了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"話說回來，在別墅裡居然會有三溫暖\n真是厲害呢。我以為這種大概只有在溫泉\n或大眾澡堂裡才會有呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"芬蘭的「Mokki」大部分都會有喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"在三溫暖室裡出了很多汗\n就出去外面讓自己涼爽下來。\n然後再進入三溫暖室裡暖和身體……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"像這樣重複進出三溫暖室非常舒服唷！\n機會難得，接下來要不要走到湖邊試試看呢？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"也是呢，薰學姊跟小巴\n好像也還要一段時間才會回來……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"……啊！？　對了！\n要在他們兩個回來之前，\n準備好烤肉的事情才行！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"要準備肉跟蔬菜……\n然後烤網還有炭火也得準備才行，再來是……\n呃、呃啊啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"小綾！？　你還好嗎！？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"啊哈哈……沒事沒事。\n只是稍微有點熱過頭了……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"果然還是到湖邊去涼快一下……\n太陽也開始下山了，\n我覺得現在的涼爽度正好適中喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"嗯～，可是……\n這麼悠哉好嗎……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"不過在三溫暖室裡暖和起來的身體，\n如果吹吹湖邊的冷風會非常舒服的說……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"嗚哇〜……感覺很棒耶……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"而且，小綾總是很努力，\n我覺得至少在旅行期間，放鬆一下也沒關係的喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"是這樣嗎……那麼，就稍微偷閒一下吧……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"啊……好涼快喔……\n這真的……有點……\n都不知道怎麼形容比較好了呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"湖畔的冷風，\n沁進身體了呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"這種感覺讓我想起了芬蘭的夏天呢……\n一邊讓溫熱的身體涼快下來，\n一邊悠哉地眺望隨著微風激起漣漪的湖面……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"仔細聆聽的話，還能聽到樹葉搖晃的沙沙聲，\n明明就很安靜，卻又充滿了大自然的聲響","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"在這期間，\n就會不知不覺地覺得自己也成為了大自然的一部分\n是非常不可思議的感覺……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"是不是因為聽不到除了我們以外的聲音呢……\n雖然也覺得有點恐怖，\n但很不可思議地不覺得討厭呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"就像是我們融進了周遭的大自然裡一樣……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev87-ep4-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlay